{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightHSLSaturationSetUnacknowledged"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightHSLSaturationSetUnacknowledged\/continueTransaction"},"metadata":{"extendedModule":"NordicMesh","roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"s:10NordicMesh18TransactionMessagePAAE08continueC0Sbvp::SYNTHESIZED::s:10NordicMesh35LightHSLSaturationSetUnacknowledgedV","title":"continueTransaction","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"continueTransaction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Whether the message should start a new transaction."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"continueTransaction"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The messages within a transaction carry the cumulative values of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a field. In case one or more messages within a transaction are not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"received by the Server (e.g., as a result of radio collisions),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the next received message will make up for the lost messages,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"carrying cumulative values of the field.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A new transaction is started when this field is set to "},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or when the last message of the transaction was sent 6 or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"more seconds earlier."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This defaults to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"text":", which means that each new message will","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"receive a new transaction identifier (if not set explicitly).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/lighthslsaturationsetunacknowledged\/continuetransaction"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/LightHSLSaturationSetUnacknowledged":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"LightHSLSaturationSetUnacknowledged"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightHSLSaturationSetUnacknowledged","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/lighthslsaturationsetunacknowledged","title":"LightHSLSaturationSetUnacknowledged","type":"topic","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"LightHSLSaturationSetUnacknowledged"}]},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh":{"abstract":[{"text":"Provision, configure and control Bluetooth mesh devices with nRF Mesh library.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"NordicMesh","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/LightHSLSaturationSetUnacknowledged/continueTransaction":{"type":"topic","title":"continueTr